{"tid":674552,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU並不是典型的美人，但卻總有一種元氣滿滿的魅力啊！","createTime":"2018-05-22T19:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T10:48:03.000Z","uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a95f0330edda32c82ca30fe84e91ba0321861916","tid":674552,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T19:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=3660802840,984160233&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=454&amp;s=5604970C0F217B1520C294D8030090BA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3660802840%2C984160233%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D454%26s%3D5604970C0F217B1520C294D8030090BA&h=65ad296b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李知恩，藝名IU，1993年5月16日出生於韓國首爾特別市，韓國女歌手、演員、主持人。2008年9月，在Mnet音樂節目《M! Countdown》中演唱歌曲《迷兒》，正式出道；隨後發行首張迷你專輯《Lost And Found》小小的好可愛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=4147610519,2729713951&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=619&amp;s=F2101D896E73569C9F2469B2030050A0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D4147610519%2C2729713951%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D619%26s%3DF2101D896E73569C9F2469B2030050A0&h=3bfc344e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2007年10月，她通過了LOEN Entertainment的試鏡，開始為期10個月的練習生生活，在此期間得到了夏東均等不少音樂人的幫助，也是很辛苦的！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LTYEUCBHs44/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FLTYEUCBHs44%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=06db802f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來，她憑借可愛的風格很快獲得了歡迎，隨後推出的《好日子》、《嘮叨》等歌曲讓她迎來了演藝事業的高峰，她的歌唱實力雄厚，其&ldquo;3段高音&rdquo;更是為人稱道，好喜歡她！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180522/a0b63fbdc87c454cab071c4f304861fb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180522%2Fa0b63fbdc87c454cab071c4f304861fb.jpeg&h=8ab13f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李知恩長得清新甜美，有著一身鄰家少女的氣質，但在音樂上卻表現強勁，她的聲音干淨、透明，教人動容，既有偶像歌手的外表也有實力歌手的天分，美不美？"},{"pid":"20cf59aad6e93ae653d516c3680f54f9f939bca0","tid":674552,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T19:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1frj2yhwlwej30sg0iyq7q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1frj2yhwlwej30sg0iyq7q.jpg&h=aee6cfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1frj7o3dpiaj30xc0lawwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1frj7o3dpiaj30xc0lawwp.jpg&h=e5bcc07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1frkk8chrfij30la0kj41x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1frkk8chrfij30la0kj41x.jpg&h=5d0b7abb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dab68ceca532053eb26ebc70c37e3540e9439a6","tid":674552,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95f0330edda32c82ca30fe84e91ba0321861916","tid":674552,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T19:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=3660802840,984160233&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=454&amp;s=5604970C0F217B1520C294D8030090BA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3660802840%2C984160233%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D454%26s%3D5604970C0F217B1520C294D8030090BA&h=65ad296b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李知恩，藝名IU，1993年5月16日出生於韓國首爾特別市，韓國女歌手、演員、主持人。2008年9月，在Mnet音樂節目《M! Countdown》中演唱歌曲《迷兒》，正式出道；隨後發行首張迷你專輯《Lost And Found》小小的好可愛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=4147610519,2729713951&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=619&amp;s=F2101D896E73569C9F2469B2030050A0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D414